// ã‚³ãƒ³ãƒ†ãƒ³ãƒ„ã®é«˜ã•ã«å¿œã˜ã¦bodyã®é«˜ã•ã‚’èª¿æ•´
function adjustBodyHeight() {
  const container = document.querySelector('.container');
  if (container) {
    // å„ã‚»ã‚¯ã‚·ãƒ§ãƒ³ã®é«˜ã•ã‚’å€‹åˆ¥ã«è¨ˆç®—
    const header = document.querySelector('.header');
    const quickActions = document.querySelector('.quick-actions');
    const groupSection = document.querySelector('.group-section');
    const createSection = document.querySelector('.create-section');
    const message = document.querySelector('.message');

    let totalHeight = 32; // containerã®padding (16px * 2)

    if (header) totalHeight += header.offsetHeight;
    if (quickActions) totalHeight += quickActions.offsetHeight;
    if (groupSection) totalHeight += groupSection.offsetHeight;
    if (createSection) totalHeight += createSection.offsetHeight;
    if (message && message.classList.contains('success') || 
        message && message.classList.contains('error') || 
        message && message.classList.contains('info')) {
      totalHeight += message.offsetHeight;
    }

    // å„è¦ç´ é–“ã®marginã‚’è€ƒæ…®ï¼ˆãŠãŠã‚ˆãã®å€¤ï¼‰
    totalHeight += 60; // å„ã‚»ã‚¯ã‚·ãƒ§ãƒ³é–“ã®margin

    const maxHeight = window.innerHeight - 50; // ã‚¦ã‚£ãƒ³ãƒ‰ã‚¦ã‚ˆã‚Šå°‘ã—å°ã•ã
    const newHeight = Math.min(totalHeight, maxHeight);
    document.body.style.height = newHeight + 'px';
  }
}

// ã‚°ãƒ«ãƒ¼ãƒ—èª­ã¿è¾¼ã¿ãŒå®Œäº†ã—ãŸã‹ã©ã†ã‹ã®ãƒ•ãƒ©ã‚°
